cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM. 

The paper proposes a novel method for improving the performance of GANs in generating images with different visual appearances. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed method involves learning the upsampling algorithm based on local context, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR). The experiments involve generating images, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
